今日は月曜日、今日明日雨降るらしい、事前に準備した方がいい。。。

折りたたみ傘どか



排汗 perspire
洗头  
整理发型 "fix my hairstyle" or "style my hair" i
刮胡子
在路上遇到 朋友  I might bump into a friend on the way,
or maybe even meet someone new. You never know!

出门 I’m heading out soon,

A: I’m heading out soon, so I’m going to wash my hair and fix my hairstyle.
B: Oh, nice! Even though you're just going out to eat by yourself?
A: Yeah, but I think it’s important to take care of how I look. I might bump into a friend on the way, or maybe even meet someone new. You never know!
B: True, you might meet someone cool!

Since I’m heading out later, I’m going to wash my hair and fix my hairstyle. Even though I’m just going out for a meal by myself, paying attention to my appearance is important. I might run into a friend on the way, or maybe even meet a potential new friend — you never know!

日语：携帯用折りたたみ傘（けいたいよう おりたたみがさ）
英语：portable folding umbrella



